description: Application for new metal railings to be installed above an existing, Grade II listed, boundary wall separating the Hackney Gardens development and St John at Hackney Churchyard Gardens.
decision_conditions:
The development hereby permitted must be begun not later than the expiration of three years beginning with the date of this permission.


REASON: In order to comply with the provisions of the Town and Country Planning Act 1990 (as amended).
subdivision_of_building: Application only concerns a small section of the listed boundary wall.
